title: A pictorial history of Western Art (Art Ebook).pdf
description:
A Pictorial History of Western Art
The New American Library | 1964 | English | 502 pages | PDF | 97 MB

This book takes the reader on a tour through about five thousand years of Western art. It begins with the origins of art in the prehistoric period and ends with the art of today. Those works of art discussed in some detail are also illustrated; all important periods and leading countries are included. Architecture, sculpture, and painting are emphasized, but the decorative arts and the graphic arts are also represented
